title: Khawaja Imran Nazir of PML-N wins PP-150 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Khawaja Imran Nazir, of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-150, Lahore-VI by securing 34,956 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Abdul Karim Khan, an Independent, who bagged 30,314 votes.
Votersâ€™ turnout remained 37.45 %.
